== Real Numbers ==

Recall that <math>\mathbb N = \{1,2,3,\ldots\}</math>.

{{question-answer|question=1. List 4 smallest elements of the set <math> \{y \mid y = 2x \mbox{ and } x \in \mathbb N\} </math>|answer={{noprint|1= 2, 4, 6, 8}}}}
{{question-answer|question=2. List 4 smallest elements of the set <math> \{z \mid z=|x+2| \mbox{ and } x \mbox{ is a negative integer}\} </math>|answer={{noprint|1= 0, 1, 2, 3}}}}
{{question-answer|question=3. If <math> A = \{0,1,2,3,4,5,6\} </math>, <math>B = \{1,3,5,7,9,11\}</math>, and <math>C = \{4,5,6,7,8\}</math>, find
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-latin;">
  <li><math>A\cup B</math></li>
  <li><math>A\cap B</math></li>
  <li><math>(A\cup B) \cap C</math></li>
  <li><math>(A\cap B) \cup (B\cap C)</math></li>
</ol>
|answer={{noprint|1=
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-latin;">
  <li><math>A\cup B = \{0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7,9,11\}</math></li>
  <li><math>A\cap B = \{1,3,5\}</math></li>
  <li><math>(A\cup B) \cap C = \{4,5,6,7\}</math></li>
  <li><math>(A\cap B) \cup (B\cap C) = \{1,3,5,7\}</math></li>
</ol>
}}}}
{{question-answer|question=4. Graph and write in a set builder notation the set <math> [0,1] \cup (2,3)</math>|answer={{noprint|1= <math> \{x \mid 0 \leq x \leq 1 \mbox{ or } 2 < x < 3\} </math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=5. Graph and write in a set builder notation the set <math> (-\infty,-1] \cup (1,\infty) </math>|answer={{noprint|1= <math> \{x \mid x \leq -1 \mbox{ or } x > 1\} </math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=6. Graph and write in a set builder notation the set <math> (-\infty,1] \cap (-1,\infty) </math>|answer={{noprint|1= <math> \{x \mid -1 < x \leq 1\} </math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=7. Evaluate given expressions if <math>x=1</math>, <math>y=-2</math>, and <math>z=3</math>
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-latin;">
  <li><math>2x^3 - y^3</math></li>
  <li><math>\displaystyle \frac{1}{x+y}(x+z)</math></li>
  <li><math>(5x+3y+z)^3</math></li>
  <li><math>\displaystyle \frac{x^2 + y^2}{z - y}</math></li>
</ol>
|answer={{noprint|1=
<ol style="list-style-type: lower-latin;">
  <li><math>10</math></li>
  <li><math>-4</math></li>
  <li><math>8</math></li>
  <li><math>1</math></li>
</ol>
}}}}

== Rational Exponents ==

