== Functions ==

{{question-answer|question=100. Given that <math>A(x) = \sqrt{x^2 + x}</math>, find <math>A(2)</math> and <math>A(r+1)</math>.|answer={{noprint|1= <math>A(2) = \sqrt6</math> and <math>A(r+1) = \sqrt{r^2 + 3r + 2}</math>.}}}}
{{question-answer|question=101. Find the domain of <math>f(x) = x + \sqrt{x-4}</math>.|answer={{noprint|1= <math>x\geq 4</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=102. Find the domain of <math>\displaystyle f(x) = \frac{1}{x+1} + \frac{1}{x-2}</math>.|answer={{noprint|1= <math>x\neq -1</math> and <math>x\neq 2</math>.}}}}
{{question-answer|question=103. Find the domain of <math>\displaystyle A(x) = \frac{\sqrt{x}}{x-1}</math>.|answer={{noprint|1= <math>[0,1)\cup(1,\infty)</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=104. Find the zeroes of <math>f(x) = (x-1)^2 - 4</math>.|answer={{noprint|1= <math>\{-1, 3\}</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=105. Find the zeroes of <math>g(x) = x^2 + 1</math>.|answer={{noprint|1= <math>\emptyset</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=106. Find the zeroes of <math>h(r) = x - 1/x</math>.|answer={{noprint|1= <math>\{-1,1\}</math>}}}}

