{{question-answer|question=255. Rewrite <math>\displaystyle \frac1{1-\sin(t)} + \frac1{1+\sin(t)}</math> in terms of a single trigonometric function or a constant. |answer={{noprint|1= <math>2\sec^2(t)</math>}}}}

