=== Usage ===

Usage: <nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|</nowiki>''name''<nowiki>}}</nowiki> generates just the part of ''name'' after the last slash.  It works by stripping off slash-separated prefixes of ''name''.

Optional named parameter <nowiki>{{{mode}}}</nowiki> varies this behavior.  If <nowiki>mode=long</nowiki>, only the first part of ''name'' is removed (up to and including the first slash), except that if there is no slash, nothing is removed.  If <nowiki>mode=split</nowiki>, the generated text is as for long mode, but a linebreak is inserted just before the last slash.

Some examples (see [[{{FULLBOOKNAME}}/Doc#Note on editing the templates|note on editing]]):

{| class="wikitable" style="width:100%;"
 ! Code
 ! Result
 ! Remark
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book/Chapter}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book/Chapter}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book/Chapter/X}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book/Chapter/X}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book/Chapter/X/Y}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book/Chapter/X/Y}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book/Chapter/X/Y/Z}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book/Chapter/X/Y/Z}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book/Chapter/X/Y/Z/W}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book/Chapter/X/Y/Z/W}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Template:</nowiki>{{BOOKNAME}}<nowiki>/Subpagename}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Template:{{BOOKNAME}}/Subpagename}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Template:</nowiki>{{BOOKNAME}}<nowiki>}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Template:{{BOOKNAME}}}}
 |doesn't remove namespace prefix
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book/A/B/C/Module|mode=long}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book/A/B/C/Module|mode=long}}
 |&#160;
 |-
 |<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|Book/A/B/C/Module|mode=split}}</nowiki>
 |{{msg:{{OBJECTPAGENAME}}|Book/A/B/C/Module|mode=split}}
 |&#160;
 |}

