=== Usage ===
<pre>
*{{fny-sn|1777|Ledum buxifolium|Bergius}}
*{{fny-sn|1888|G. nivalis|ssp=imperati|Baker}}
</pre>

yields:

*{{fny-sn|1777|Ledum buxifolium|Bergius}}
