=== Thinking concurrently === 		 
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|4.1.14|Identify the parts of a solution that could be implemented concurrently.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|4.1.15|Describe how concurrent processing can be used to solve a problem.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|4.1.16|Evaluate the decision to use concurrent processing in solving a problem.}}

Concurrent processing allows for faster computation, as multiple tasks are run simultaneously. However, concurrent processing is a lot more difficult to program.

