{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|D.2.4|Explain the advantages of encapsulation.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|D.2.5|Explain the advantages of inheritance.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|D.2.6|Explain the advantages of polymorphism.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|D.2.7|Describe the advantages of libraries of objects.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|D.2.8|Describe the disadvantages of OOP.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|D.2.9|Discuss the use of programming teams.}}
{{IB_Computer_Science/Statement|D.2.10|Explain the advantages of modularity in program development.}}

